中心的万达广场闲逛，结果，路过位于负一楼的永辉超市许昌万达广场店（下称“永辉万达店”）时，却看到一张“停业公告”。 “本店将于2024年4月8日停止营业…”永辉万达店在上述公告中称。 之后，虽然市场有消息称，永辉万达店的停业，是由于许昌万达广场内部调整所致，但在汪海洋等许昌本地人看来，距离胖东来天使城太近，进而导致其不少顾客被不断分流，或许是永辉万达店停业的一个重要原因。 第一财经记者查询发现，永辉万达店开业于2018年11月30日，而开业于2023年初的胖东来天使城，与其之间的直线距离仅有一两公里。不仅如此，在其周边，还有距离约3公里的胖东来时代广场，以及距离不到2公里的胖东来云鼎店，可以说，从当初的开业起，永辉万达店就处于胖东来门店的“重重包围”之中。商业秘密｜胖东来“阴影”下的许昌零售业：有的停业倒闭，有的“胖东来化”"},"attached_info":"CkAIm4WQ87XVw9hCEAMaCTEwODM3NTU3OCCm+dWyBjAAOIYGQCFyCTY1NzQzOTkzMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"48 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-51f0b95127eb39d4868c37ecfb068d81_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"34_1717017400.346058","card_id":"Q_657175222","target":{"id":657175222,"title":"《庆余年》中范闲的几个爹明知道是庆帝杀了叶轻眉，为什么不联手直接杀庆帝？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/657175222","type":"question","created":1716660095,"answer_count":68,"follower_count":172,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2102,108750,140022,665819],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAIm4WQ87XVw9hCEAMaCTEwODMxNjk4NCD/zsiyBjAAOKwBQCJyCTY1NzE3NTIyMngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"46 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-5e1fea2dbfcd54a61cca925cefe00d78_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"35_1717017400.346269","card_id":"Q_657041007","target":{"id":657041007,"title":"如果还能做回小朋友，你最想去做的一件事情是什么？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/657041007","type":"question","created":1716547156,"answer_count":58,"follower_count":79,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1395,16779,1378164,3420385,3507594],"comm